"Field names are case-insensitive. Supported formats: mp3, ogg, flac, "
"opus, aac/m4a and others supported by mutagen. When combined with "
"<code>{im:…}</code> or <code>{vi:…}</code>, non-matching fields are "
"silently empty. With only <code>{au:…}</code> fields, a default is "
"recommended."
